title: Hit the Road!
description: Time to leave Vilnius behind! Flexible departure depending on when everyone's ready for the scenic hour drive.

title: Arrival at Lake Paradise
description: Welcome to Moletai! Simple, warm welcome to our lakeside adventure base after the pleasant drive.

title: Campfire & Music
description: Guitars, stories, and quiet chats by the fire. Bring a blanket; stay for the stars.

title: Slow Breakfast Start
description: Rise and shine, Lithuania! Keep it easy, keep it social, keep it delicious.

title: Lithuanian Landing Party
description: The Lithuanians have arrived! Time for welcome drinks and the real party to begin.

title: Meet & Greet
description: Names, laughs, and who's who. Fast intros, friendly faces.

title: Mixed-Culture Quiz Battle
description: Slovenians vs Lithuanians? Nah! Mixed teams for maximum cultural chaos and fun!

title: Freedom Hour
description: Hammocks, lake dips, a nap—or do nothing at all.

title: Lunch Together
description: Plates up, stories down the table. Recharge for the afternoon.

title: Park Explorer Mission
description: Guided tour of the park - perfect for digesting lunch with some light movement and nature vibes.

title: Water & Games
description: Cannonballs, frisbee, and cold drinks nearby.

title: Snacks & Reset
description: Top up snacks, change shirts, breathe, and reset.

title: Evening Program
description: Lights down, playlist up—dance if you want.

title: Slow Motion Morning
description: Wake up slowly with coffee, quiet music, and peaceful morning walks. No rush, just vibes.

title: Brunch & Heart-to-Hearts
description: The perfect time to eat, chat, and soak in those last precious moments together.

title: Pack-Up & Memory Lane
description: Last hugs, final photos, and maybe some guestbook signing for the memories!

title: Road Trip Back to Vilnius
description: Hugs, bags, and one last wave. Safe drive back to Vilnius.
